                            >This is consistent with the anticipated result.</p>
                            <p id="fs-idm28230576">
                              <span data-type="title">Check Your Learning</span>
                              What is the mass of 0.443 mol of hydrazine, N
                              <sub>2</sub>H
                              <sub>4</sub>?
